                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Backend Development -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card mb-3" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="card-header px-3 py-2">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="h5 mb-1">Backend Development</h3>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/services/dotnet.svg" width="48" height="48"
                                 alt="Backend Development"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body px-3 py-2">
                        <p>I have extensive experience in backend development using .NET Core and .NET Framework,
                            specializing
                            in RESTful API
                            design, Microservices architecture, and scalable backend solutions.
                        </p>

                        <p>My expertise includes ASP.NET Core Web API, Minimal
                            APIs, Entity Framework Core, Dapper, and gRPC, ensuring high-performance applications. I am
                            well-versed in design
                            patterns (SOLID, DDD) and clean architecture, making maintainable and efficient codebases.
