                                 alt="Microservices & Messaging"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body px-3 py-2">

                        <p>I have worked extensively on event-driven architecture using RabbitMQ, and Azure Service Bus,
                            implementing
                            reliable messaging between microservices.
                        </p>
                        <p>My experience includes service discovery (Consul, API Gateway), distributed
                            tracing (OpenTelemetry), and fault-tolerant communication for scalable distributed systems.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Software Architecture & Best Practices -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card mb-3" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="card-header px-3 py-2">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="h5 mb-1">Software Architecture & Best Practices</h3>
