                                 alt="Software Architecture & Best Practices"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body px-3 py-2">

                        <p>I have a strong understanding of software design principles, including SOLID, Clean Code, and
                            Domain-Driven Design
                            (DDD).
                        </p>
                        <p>I have experience implementing CQRS, Event Sourcing, and Hexagonal Architecture to build
                            scalable
                            and
                            maintainable applications.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Testing & Quality Assurance -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card mb-3" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="card-header px-3 py-2">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="h5 mb-1">Testing & Quality Assurance</h3>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/services/testing.svg" width="48" height="48"
                                 alt="Testing & Quality Assurance"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body px-3 py-2">

                        <p>I am skilled in unit testing (XUnit, NUnit), integration testing, and test automation to
                            ensure
                            software reliability.
                        </p>
                        <p> My experience includes mocking frameworks (Moq, FakeItEasy), API testing, and CI/CD test
                            automation for continuous quality assurance.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Agile & Team Collaboration -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card mb-3" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="card-header px-3 py-2">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="h5 mb-1">Agile & Team Collaboration</h3>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/services/teamwork.svg" width="48" height="48"
                                 alt="Agile & Team Collaboration"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body px-3 py-2">

                        <p>I have worked in Scrum and Agile environments, using Azure Boards, Jira, and Confluence for
                            project
                            management. </p>
                        <p>I am experienced in collaborating with cross-functional teams, conducting code reviews, and
                            mentoring junior developers to
                            improve overall team efficiency.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@code {
    private bool _isVisible = true;
    private string _toggleClass = "expanded";

    private void ToggleDiv()
    {
        _isVisible = !_isVisible;
        _toggleClass = _isVisible ? "expanded" : "collapsed";
    }
}